svg.text: Wang Peng and Li You had a fight. The two of them haven’t seen each other, called, texted,
or chatted online for a while now. In pairs, form a question-and-answer about their strained
relationship based on the images, e.g.:
李友多长时间没跟王朋见面了？
Lǐ Yǒu duō cháng shíjiān méi gēn Wáng Péng jiàn miàn le?
李友一个星期没跟王朋见面了。
Lǐ Yǒu yí ge xīngqī méi gēn Wáng Péng jiàn miàn le.
